The paper deals with the problem of detecting important people in images, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves constructing a graph and using algorithms to infer the most active node, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of the PageRank algorithm also suggests a focus on algorithms and machine learning (cs.LG). The datasets used in the paper are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as they involve images and sports game sequences.
